        "h3": { "en": "Thread on the gooseneck", "zh": "拧上金属软管" },
        "body": { "en": "Spin the gooseneck's female end onto the stud, snug against the hex nut. The free male end takes the camera next.", "zh": "把金属软管的内螺纹一端拧到螺柱上，紧贴住六角螺母。空着的外螺纹一端，下一步装摄像头。" },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:140mm; top:80mm; width:60mm;"
      }
